---
// src/components/Equipo.astro
---
<section class="py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-primary font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">El equipo detrás del éxito</h2>
            <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight">Sobre <span class="italic underline decoration-primary">EXPERT.ADS</span></h3>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-square">
                    <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500" data-alt="Portrait of Caro, Co-founder of Expert.Ads" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCpI3xOl-QVGPx6K1Rk5H0jUK6aYkOzpgdS8_XkaHDgo3MWsk-KtbLvwCpufvHirJQVlQ_zfipuavztWnxafXvsPUuNpo9hDITQaFgrE-eXsHfwQyBt0f_nDfkzzh-sEYc-KWhvxkftY-8R3EJ9B2dnbcNZfiyFnboIlIgXRDd7YJuLESXnCZ4r9-zSojcFVAJ2cdkmgx0ftQuh0A4Rz1OTtQWzYauJJPskpNwVG8TmRq3u0veaWA25vjsBwypP6OWRPniYEcbDWd8"/>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6 p-6 glass-card rounded-xl">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold">Caro</h4>
                        <p class="text-primary font-bold">Estratega de Tráfico Pago</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <blockquote class="text-xl italic text-slate-400 border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 py-2 leading-relaxed">
                    "Mi enfoque está en los números y la optimización. No paramos hasta que el sistema es rentable y escalable."
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-square">
                    <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500" data-alt="Portrait of Dai, Co-founder of Expert.Ads" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCzeP94H-kKwdKUSSvcDcOqZQmONetUk8VvectMpI5NKaROTPxgNmzSgZEFT1GzAOWqngQXMGJpY7LFNWpcCaDHIOC5eazbUT6x80TgtejoHWWptlLn2UQzWQtnsMoi4O2YsXbQTG1SdOvSCWn1PdGThUc9nXcWCCG9yGL4sxd-fCMbbpFm00Pt9b3DHPcxhO_8xh8_vJ5Lv9ND5dhlW_5GJ9mN6MkOJuM6XPkdBLekCEKK36geayg4lk8dPCLqbQC7uRkD_uay4BE"/>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6 p-6 glass-card rounded-xl">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold">Dai</h4>
                        <p class="text-primary font-bold">Directora Creativa y de Estrategia</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <blockquote class="text-xl italic text-slate-400 border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 py-2 leading-relaxed">
                    "La comunicación es el puente. Unimos la esencia de tu marca con creativos que realmente convierten."
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>